title: #92Noon! 10a Hour 2/16 - Arif Hasan/Howl
description: Arif Hasan is with PA to discuss the road ahead for the Vikings as the make personnel decisions and manage the '22 cap. Then Wolves discussion, followed by an update by MN Senator Roger Chamberlain on legalizing sports betting in the state!
